            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "copying my comment from chat so it doesn't get lost:\r\n\r\nNot sure we need so much granularity. One flag for `visual` and one for outside of viewport for any reason (so all of leftcol,skipcol,rightcol in one flag) might be enough to start with.",
